title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Chemical Products
description: Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Chemical Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 410.80 GBP Million in September from 499.37 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Chemical Products in the United Kingdom averaged 189.80 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 680.38 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 53.70 GBP Million in December of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Chemical Prod.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
